bilingual.source: We must quickly deploy the rescue team.
bilingual.target: 我们必须迅速部署救援队。

bilingual.source: The military will deploy troops to the border.
bilingual.target: 军方将部署部队到边境。

bilingual.source: The IT team will deploy the servers tonight.
bilingual.target: IT团队将在今晚部署服务器。

bilingual.source: They decided to deploy the new marketing strategy.
bilingual.target: 他们决定部署新的营销策略。

bilingual.source: This software is easy to deploy on the server.
bilingual.target: 这个软件很容易部署到服务器上。

bilingual.source: The manager decided to deploy a new sales strategy.
bilingual.target: 经理决定部署新的销售策略。

bilingual.source: The company plans to deploy new software next month.
bilingual.target: 公司计划下个月部署新软件。

bilingual.source: We need to deploy more resources to handle the situation.
bilingual.target: 我们需要部署更多资源来处理这种情况。

bilingual.source: We need to deploy more resources to complete this project.
bilingual.target: 我们需要部署更多的资源来完成这个项目。

bilingual.source: gtm allows you to deploy marketing tags quickly.
bilingual.target: gtm（Google Tag Manager， 谷歌代码管理器）允许你快速部署营销标签。

list.abstract: 散开是一个汉语词语，拼音是sàn kāi，意思是分散，向四处分散。也是一种军事术语。

yingyinNormal.en: Which is where we need to go to deploy the countermeasure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我们要去那里部署对策。

yingyinNormal.en: The CDC's new Ebola rapid response teams will deploy quickly to help hospitals implement the right protocols.
yingyinNormal.zh: 疾控中心新的快速反应小组将迅速部署，帮助各医院实施正确的方案。

yingyinNormal.en: After a long day, we can come home, because they're willing to leave their families and deploy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 经过一整天，我们可以回家因为他们愿意离开他们的家人，并被派遣到其他地方。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the absolute soonest you can deploy? Twelve hours, Mr. President. But that would involve an extremely high degree…
yingyinNormal.zh: 那调派最快需要多久？12小时，总统先生。但这涉及极高的……

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: On June 7 Google pledged not to "design or <highlight>deploy</highlight> AI" that would cause "overall harm," .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 6月7日，谷歌承诺不会“设计或部署会造成“全面伤害”的人工智能。

examination_example.sentence: It also pledged not to <highlight>deploy</highlight> AI whose use would violate international laws or human rights.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它还承诺不部署其使用将违反国际法或人权的人工智能。

word_family.mean: v. 部署；利用；展开；部署行动；有效使用

examination_example.sentence: The problem with <highlight>deploying</highlight> machine learning and artificial intelligence in agriculture is not that scientists lack the capacity to develop programs and protocols.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在农业中部署机器学习和人工智能的问题并不在于科学家缺乏开发程序和协议的能力。

examination_example.sentence: Multiples can be <highlight>deployed</highlight> in combination for more complex missions than could be achieved by one CubeSat alone.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 多个卫星可以组合运用，以执行比一个立方体卫星更复杂的任务。

examination_example.sentence: This decrease in cost allows researchers and even hobbyists to put simple instruments into LEO or even having them <highlight>deployed</highlight> from the ISS.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这一成本的降低使得研究人员甚至业余爱好者都可以将简单的仪器送入近地轨道，甚至可以在国际空间站部署它们。

examination_example.sentence: This is because the more technology is put into the field, the more people are needed to <highlight>deploy</highlight>, maintain and improve it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是因为投入到该领域的技术越多，就需要越多的人来部署、维护和改进它。
